edule.\n    *   `2.0`: Best for **4K**.\n    *   `1.0`: Best for **2K**.\n    *   `0.5`: Best for **~1.5K**.\n*   **`yarn_alt_scaling`**: *(Legacy `yarn` only)* Switch between Anisotropic (Sharper, potential stretching) and Isotropic (Softer, accurate geometry).\n*   **`base_shift` / `max_shift`**: Advanced noise schedule controls. Defaults (`0.5` / `1.15`) are optimized for FLUX.\n\n\n## Join\n\n### [TokenDiffusion](https://t.me/TokenDiff) - AI for every home, creativity for every mind!\n\n### [TokenDiff Community Hub](https://t.me/TokenDiff_hub) - Questions, help, and thoughtful discussion. "],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":38,"type":"SmartLatentGenerator","pos":[929.9247076861741,470.9425007622665],"size":[270,106],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"resolution_preset","name":"resolution_preset","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"resolution_preset"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"aspect_ratio","name":"aspect_ratio","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"aspect_ratio"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"batch_size","name":"batch_size","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"batch_size"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"LATENT","name":"LATENT","type":"LATENT","links":[68]}],"properties":{"aux_id":"buddy-bytes/ComfyUI-SmartResolutionToolkit","ver":"e96df2edc0074dddd7e5201b17d9b327fa65ad94","Node name for S&R":"SmartLatentGenerator","widget_ue_connectable":{}},"widgets_values":["4K-3840px","2:3-ClassicPortrait",1]},{"id":6,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[409.4903352349137,88.1537641321548],"size":[441.3974093064526,420.15306375882255],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":43},{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"CONDITIONING","name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","slot_index":0,"links":[4]}],"title":"CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.67","Node n